{"tid":708422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奪命地盤】國土局局長帶老婆睇樓 遭天降建材扑死","createTime":"2018-06-19T09:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T12:25:01.000Z","uid":176366,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8ff30c3e86d2c56368a66d5c26e664177cf3a3","tid":708422,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"廣東省江門市蓬江區星滙名庭四期建築地盤，前日（16日）下午4時多發生奪命意外，原本正向上吊起的施工材料突然掉落，1名售樓人員與3名前來睇樓的客人正好路過，被砸個正着，造成1人死亡，3人受傷。內地媒體今日報道，指經江門市委宣傳部證實，死者為國土局局長。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，4人隨即被送院救治。據悉，其中1名傷者手腕受傷，目前正在江門市五邑中醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述知情街坊說，星滙名庭四期開放給市民看樓，已有幾個月時間，與此同時，樓盤也同步在進行施工。街坊說，這次意外是吊貨物的繩子斷了，導致貨物跌落所致。<br />\n<br />\n事發當晚，江門市蓬江區政府發佈通告稱，當時林姓夫婦、溫X隨樓盤銷售人員王X共4人前去睇樓，從售樓部到樣辦房途中遭遇事故。隨後，4人被立即被送往醫院，林X經搶救無效死亡。目前，另外3名傷者暫無生命危險。經初步調查，該項目施工單位為廣東省第二建築工程有限公司。事故發生後，住建部門已責令事故地盤及涉事企業其他地盤全面停工。昨日，江門全市也開展了地盤安全檢查和整治行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180618/58333319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F58333319&d=IYB1KEC4QVtgI8ppafVNdozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b15b1947\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F58333319&h=ece18d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180618/58333319</a><br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045ba493dfb0295a5491388b9025850e270eea31","tid":708422,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"整定🤷&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"685383851a69ff34b27daa3f6b4555b6e9585cbe","tid":708422,"uid":29540,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"0016d6c3b8c3a5d77298540a4e4a5d3583db01ba","tid":708422,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"正評不解釋"},{"pid":"c4270dc84bdacca0324f0051bd17aad1d34ebe66","tid":708422,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10523c7cb00a2533df4907dc4c36c656dd66e3f6","tid":708422,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169bf3214d593d262d84f4d19e8be09a068abefc","tid":708422,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:28:37.000Z","m